SF Dockside from America's Army

52 spawn points

2 Hostages(inside and on a boat inside one of the crates), 2 Bombsites(roof and on the side of the map with no boats)

I took out some stuff from the AA version to improve FPS, playing with 40+ players could get a little laggy(FPS wise) but I haven't tested it with that many people yet.


If you find any bugs please post about them and I'll try to fix them ASAP.
GIJOE92
